Package org.nvonop.selenium.framework.controls.interfaces

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Clickable
    This interface allows a user to configure UI controls with click functionality.
    Detectable
    This interface allows a user to configure UI controls with functionality to determine whether or not the control is visible.
    Form
    This interface allows a user to configure UI controls with functionality to fill in a form with data.
    Readable
    This interface allows a user to configure UI controls with functionality to read the text of the control.
    Selectable
    This interface provides functionality for selecting and deselecting a control.
    Writeable
    This interface provides functionality for writing data into a control.
